  <body>
    <div xml:id="Aink120">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>amma vāḻi tōḻi nalamika</l>
<l>nalla vāyiṉa vaḷiyameṉ ṟōḷē</l>
<l>malla liruṅkaḻi nīraṟal viriyu</l>
<l>mellam pulampaṉ vanta māṟē</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Oh friend, listen!</l>
<l>The pitiable, soft shoulders have become greatly well</l>
<l>[Because of] the change in which the Lord of the tender, pretty, maritime tract</l>
<l>In which the abundant, great backwaters expand,</l>
<l>Came [back].</l>
</lg>
    </div>
